===CONMEBOL–UEFA Cup of Champions===
After winning a record fourth European Championship in 2024, Spain qualified to their first ever CONMEBOL–UEFA Cup of Champions, where they were scheduled to face [[Argentina national football team|Argentina]], the champions of the [[2024 Copa América]]. However, the match was later cancelled after both sides could not come to an agreement as to which stadium would host the game.

